her.gov.sg/warning-tropical-cyclone-information/">Tropical Cyclone Information</a></h3>                                        </div>                                        <div class="menu-group">                                            <h3><a href="http://www.weather.gov.sg/warning-regional-seismic-information/">Regional Earthquake/Tsunami</a></h3>                                        </div>                                        <div class="menu-group">                                            <h3><a href="http://www.weather.gov.sg/warning-volcanic-eruption/">Regional Volcanic Eruptions </a></h3>                                        </div>                                    </div>                                </div>                            </div>                            <!-- / .dropdown-menu -->                        </li>                        <li>                            <a href="#" class="dropdown-toggle" data-toggle="dropdown">Climate</a>                            <div class="dropdown-menu" role="menu">                                <div class="row">                                    <div class="col-xs-4">                                        <div class="menu-group">                                            <h3><a href="http://www.weather.gov.sg/climate-historical-daily/">Historical Daily Records </a></h3>                                        </div>                                        <div class="menu-group">                                            <h3>Historical Extremes</h3>                                            <ul>                                                <li><a href="http://www.weather.gov.sg/climate-historical-extremes/">Rainfall</a></li>                                                <li><a href="http://www.weather.gov.sg/climate-historical-extremes-temperature/">Temperature</a></li>                                                <li><a href="http://www.weather.gov.sg/climate-historical-extremes-humidity/